(158,	1,	'2017-06-09 11:20:10',	'2017-06-09 08:20:10',	'Research and Survey Institute GEOTECH takes part at the largest international exhibition of high-tech «CHINA HI-TECH FAIR» which be held in Shenzhen, China, on 16-21 November, 2014. Research and Survey Institute GEOTECH will feature a presentation of new technical solutions and demonstrate the equipment at the Russian exposition, organized by the Ministry of Education and Science of Russia. Visitors will be able to see Constrcution Scan-1700 and other products.\r\n\r\nCHTF has been held since 1999, and by the end of the first decade of its existence, it was recognized as the largest and the most important event in the field of science and high technology in China.\r\n\r\nCHTF program includes an exhibition of high technology, and business meetings with investors, as well as, since 2003, the multinational forum of senior state officials.',	'CHINA HI-TECH FAIR',	'',	'publish',	'closed',	'closed',	'',	'china-hi-tech-fair',	'',	'',	'2017-06-09 12:50:08',	'2017-06-09 09:50:08',	'',	0,	'http://geotech.3331141.xeovo.ml/?post_type=news&#038;p=158',	0,	'news',	'',	0),
